	 </english-overview>		
	 <english-features>
		<ul>
			<li>Usenet like threaded tree structure of the messages.</li><br />
			<li>Different views of the threads possible (classical, table, folded).</li><br />
			<li>Categories and tags.</li><br />
			<li>BB codes and smilies.</li><br />
			<li>Image upload.</li><br />
			<li>Avatars.</li><br />
			<li>RSS Feeds.</li><br />
			<li>Template engine(Smarty).</li><br />
			<li>Different methods of spam protection.</li><br />
